          l’emballage ;-) )
          Sodium cocoate**, Sambucus nigra flower water*, Sodium
          sunflowerseedate**, Sodium olivate**, Glycerin**, Sodium shea
          butterate**, Almond oil*, Calendula officinalis flower*

